Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:49.23,OP,,0,0,0,,例えば目が覚めて「すべては幻だ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:55.41,OP,,0,0,0,,奇跡めいた妄想を叶えて欲しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.12,OP,,0,0,0,,僕が描いた罪で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.79,OP,,0,0,0,,結末を満たさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:22.64,OP,,0,0,0,,壊し続けた僕は何かを救えた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:28.73,OP,,0,0,0,,変わり果てた今に革命のナイフ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}ほどけるように刺して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:36.78,OP,,0,0,0,,光に満ちたさよならを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.37,OP,,0,0,0,,I will miss you, I will miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}罰を僕に与えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:50.46,OP,,0,0,0,,君はまだ僕を愛してはくれるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:56.67,OP,,0,0,0,,「僕じゃなきゃ」「僕じゃダメだ」「僕じゃなきゃ」がループする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:02:03.01,OP,,0,0,0,,僕を刺したナイフさえも  いつかきっと光を射すから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:49.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,希望某天醒来 发现一切都是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:55.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我多想这种奇迹般的妄想能成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不要让我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,成为故事的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:22.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,破坏众多存在的我 又拯救了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:28.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,给面目全非的如今 一场革命的刀光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}仿佛要彻底获得解脱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:36.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,渴求那个充满光明的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}给我应有的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:50.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,你仍旧愿意爱我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:56.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,陷入「非我不可」「我不行的」「非我不可」的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:02:03.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,刺向我的刀光 迟早也会毁灭那片光明
Comment: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,/----04----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来助阵 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:14.32,Comments,,0,0,0,,美食家\NS等级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是这个样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就会让你想起来的 啼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那位先生不同 我对自己的记忆力很有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该有笔账要和你算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩猎青桐终于是有成果了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人好找啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:00.95,Comments,,0,0,0,,大蛇\NS等级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 他的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头疼 这里可不是什么迷路儿童看护中心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要做成这样 用女搜查官的身体多好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宗交待过我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔可不能让你带走哦 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是条没礼貌的尾巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就来管教你吧 萝玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 肯定被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银喰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就...结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷泽...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:43.55,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(340,463.667)}遗留之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷泽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真户准特等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真户 你这是做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包庇喰种吗 是条重罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我极力想让自己冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没资格当搜查官啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷泽 我真的想过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我在那时...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真户 真户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚门先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去她会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带她走 政道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去...去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去码头 同伴在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚门先生 你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真以为我会救真户吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背叛了你们 是个杀人犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚门先生 我并不认为这样自己就算被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有句话是叫寡不敌众吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可得抓紧时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然嘉纳先生就要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰啰嗦嗦烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种拼命的人看起来真的超搞笑啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萝玛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你 眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫锦 平胸女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿髭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要把真户淮特等怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CCG不是她该待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一介喰种 胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大喊大叫会暴露攻击的 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手感如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没命中赫包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了 居然对女孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事 给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小死堪 用翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低下头 平胸女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙有两种赫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死堪虽然一副呆样 但却有着特别的赫包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 优势还在我们这边哦 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 你不觉得相互争斗是件很空虚的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长 这个喰种的所有权...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的职责是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米林 我已经不想再失去同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远程启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长 去追猫头鹰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样子不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫子的异常增大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共喰的混蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,框架3解放 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,髭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,髭丸 各位...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想...失去任何人...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许杀班长 不许杀我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是什么 为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那时候要救才子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那时我认为那么做是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫米林是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界已经扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是正确的 什么又是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍不留神就会无法辨别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要停止思考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去想想你做出的选择究竟是对是错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思 这可不好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以自己的方式调查了和修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书中所主张的 和修家是喰种的协力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和修家并不是什么喰种的协力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是喰种本身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有决定性证据就把枪口对向我了吗 阿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我一个老朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不喜欢这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这只是件单纯的杀人案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太失望了 阿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让你们攻破
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的库克利亚 我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SS小丑的牢房里都空无一人了啊 监狱长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去迎接王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就不剩多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是提早迎来了死亡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有马先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 金木研
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和入 还有旧多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些白日庭出生的搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内混杂着喰种之血 是不完整的半人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的右眼 相信你已经察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经基本看不到任何东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青光眼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:17:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对老年人来就是很常见的病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老年人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道人类与喰种之间生下的孩子会怎么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成独眼喰种 或者半喰种?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是所有人都那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生的孩子和人类基本没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的只是身体素质比常人更强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及比较短命这两点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独眼枭那种例子是非常罕见的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们比正常人类老化更快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我另一只眼睛的视力也在逐渐弱化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的寿命已经快走到尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么会这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是和修他们想尽量成为人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和修家...CCG的领导是喰种?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情况去问丈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把一切都跟他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有马先生 希望我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我杀了独眼之王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对外就说是你杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有马先生就是独眼之王...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果存在能够杀死有马贵将的喰种
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将成为喰种们的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱支是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独眼之王是我和爱支共同创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是只有你才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 是我亲手杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很讨厌...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会不断掠夺的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次总算感觉留下了些什么
